title: >>> DROP that BOMB
body_text: Here is your DODGEBALL 18 & 19 Double Promotional Poster completed not by KJohn Tronolone, but by Hall of Famer Dan Spengeman. Dan becomes just the second man in dodgeball history to successfully create a logo for an event.
